270 inline bool TrajectoryGenerator::isScalingFactorValid(const double& scaling_factor)
271 {
272  return (scaling_factor > MIN_SCALING_FACTOR && scaling_factor <= MAX_SCALING_FACTOR);
273 }
274 
275 inline bool TrajectoryGenerator::isCartesianGoalGiven(const moveit_msgs::Constraints& constraint)
276 {
277  return constraint.position_constraints.size() == 1 && constraint.orientation_constraints.size() == 1;
278 }
279 
280 inline bool TrajectoryGenerator::isJointGoalGiven(const moveit_msgs::Constraints& constraint)
281 {
282  return !constraint.joint_constraints.empty();
283 }
284 
285 inline bool TrajectoryGenerator::isOnlyOneGoalTypeGiven(const moveit_msgs::Constraints& constraint)
286 {
287  return (isJointGoalGiven(constraint) && !isCartesianGoalGiven(constraint)) ||
288  (!isJointGoalGiven(constraint) && isCartesianGoalGiven(constraint));
289 }
